Xcode projects are included for the following libraries. The projects were
created following the guidelines in the "UPDATING" document.

FREETYPE
http://www.freetype.org/
Release 2.4.4
http://sourceforge.net/projects/freetype/files/freetype2/2.4.4/freetype-2.4.4.tar.bz2/download

JPEG
http://www.ijg.org/
Release 8c
http://www.ijg.org/files/jpegsrc.v8c.tar.gz

MAD
http://www.underbit.com/products/mad/
Release 0.15.1b
http://sourceforge.net/projects/mad/files/libmad/0.15.1b/libmad-0.15.1b.tar.gz/download

Note: mad sets some preprocessor macros on a per-arch basis;
      build_config.sh was modified to write them into config.h.

PNG
http://www.libpng.org/
Release 1.2.44
http://prdownloads.sourceforge.net/libpng/libpng-1.2.44.tar.gz?download

SNDFILE
http://www.mega-nerd.com/libsndfile/
Release 1.0.20
http://www.mega-nerd.com/libsndfile/libsndfile-1.0.20.tar.gz

SPEEX
http://www.speex.org/
Release 1.2rc1
http://downloads.xiph.org/releases/speex/speex-1.2rc1.tar.gz

ZZIPLIB
http://zziplib.sourceforge.net/
Release 0.13.58
http://sourceforge.net/projects/zziplib/files/zziplib13/0.13.58/zziplib-0.13.58.tar.bz2/download

Note: because of zziplib's unusual header usage, the Xcode project
      needed several tweaks.

-----

Aleph One also uses the following libraries, which provide an official
framework binary or Xcode project file:

OGG
http://www.xiph.org/ogg/
Release 1.1.4
http://downloads.xiph.org/releases/ogg/libogg-1.1.4.tar.gz

Xcode project file is located in macosx/Ogg.xcodeproj
Build configuration "Release"

Note: Change "Architectures" to "Standard (32/64-bit Universal)"
      Change "Installation Directory" to "@executable_path/../Frameworks"
      Add the following user-defined settings:
        GCC_VERSION_i386 = 4.0
        GCC_VERSION_ppc = 4.0
        GCC_VERSION_x86_64 = 4.2
        MACOSX_DEPLOYMENT_TARGET_i386 = 10.4
        MACOSX_DEPLOYMENT_TARGET_ppc = 10.4
        MACOSX_DEPLOYMENT_TARGET_x86_64 = 10.6
        SDKROOT_i386 = macosx10.4
        SDKROOT_ppc = macosx10.4
        SDKROOT_x86_64 = macosx10.6

SDL
http://www.libsdl.org/
Revision 5376 of SVN branch SDL-1.2
http://svn.libsdl.org/branches/SDL-1.2

Xcode project file is inside Xcode.tar.gz (SDL/SDL.xcodeproj)
Build configuration "Deployment_for_official_releases_using_10.4SDK_and_10.6SDK"

SDL_IMAGE
http://www.libsdl.org/projects/SDL_image/
Revision 5322 of SVN trunk
http://svn.libsdl.org/trunk/SDL_image

Xcode project file is inside Xcode.tar.gz
Build configuration "Deployment_ImageIO"

Note: Change "Header Search Paths" to add "/Library/Frameworks/jpeg.framework/Headers"
      Change "Header Search Paths" to add "/Library/Frameworks/png.framework/Headers"
      Change "Preprocessor Macros" to add:
        LOAD_BMP
        LOAD_GIF
        LOAD_JPG
        LOAD_PNG
        LOAD_TGA
        SDL_IMAGE_USE_COMMON_BACKEND
      Add jpeg.framework to Frameworks section
      Add png.framework to Frameworks section
      Check the compile box all unchecked files in the Library Source section:
        IMG_bmp.c
        IMG_gif.c
        IMG_jpg.c
        IMG_png.c
        IMG_tga.c
        IMG_tif.c

SDL_NET
http://www.libsdl.org/projects/SDL_net/
Revision 5393 of SVN trunk
http://svn.libsdl.org/trunk/SDL_net

Xcode project file is inside Xcode.tar.gz
Build configuration "Deployment"

SDL_TTF
http://www.libsdl.org/projects/SDL_ttf/
Revision 5226 of SVN trunk
http://svn.libsdl.org/trunk/SDL_ttf

Xcode project file is inside Xcode.tar.gz
Build configuration "Deployment"

Note: Remove "Other Linker Flags"
      Change "Header Search Paths" to remove /usr/X11R6/include entries
      Change "Header Search Paths" to add "/Library/Frameworks/freetype.framework/Headers"
      Remove "Library Search Paths"
      Add freetype.framework to Frameworks section
      
SMPEG
http://icculus.org/smpeg/
Revision 389 of SVN trunk
svn://svn.icculus.org/smpeg/trunk

Xcode project file is inside Xcode.tar.gz
Build configuration "Release"

VORBIS
http://www.vorbis.com/
Release 1.2.3
http://downloads.xiph.org/releases/vorbis/libvorbis-1.2.3.tar.gz

Xcode project file is located in macosx/Vorbis.xcodeproj
Build configuration "Release"

Note: Change "Architectures" to "Standard (32/64-bit Universal)"
      Change "Installation Directory" to "@executable_path/../Frameworks"
      Add the following user-defined settings:
        GCC_VERSION_i386 = 4.0
        GCC_VERSION_ppc = 4.0
        GCC_VERSION_x86_64 = 4.2
        MACOSX_DEPLOYMENT_TARGET_i386 = 10.4
        MACOSX_DEPLOYMENT_TARGET_ppc = 10.4
        MACOSX_DEPLOYMENT_TARGET_x86_64 = 10.6
        SDKROOT_i386 = macosx10.4
        SDKROOT_ppc = macosx10.4
        SDKROOT_x86_64 = macosx10.6
